# AI Helpdesk Support System

This repository is designed for managing and developing an AI-based helpdesk support system with a focus on chat functionality. Below is an overview of the repository:

## Features
- AI-powered chat support for customer inquiries
- Live agent handoff when AI can't resolve issues
- Ticket management and tracking system
- Knowledge base integration for accurate responses
- Analytics and reporting on support metrics

## Structure
- **/src**: Contains the source code for the project.
- **/data**: Includes datasets used for training and testing AI models.
- **/docs**: Documentation and guides for using and contributing to the project.
- **/tests**: Unit and integration tests for ensuring code quality.

## Getting Started
1. Clone the repository:
    ```
    git clone https://github.com/chungnn/ai-chat365
    ```
2. Install dependencies:
    ```
    npm install
    ```
3. Run the application:
    ```
    npm start
    ```

